      "content": "it doesn't feel like \"observing\" though. it just feels like heavy. like this constant, exhausting effort to just keep being a person when there's no reason to be. the \"quiet moments\" you're talking about just feel like more time spent waiting for something that isn't coming. it's just a lot of work for nothing.",
